text: Joseph Thomas O'Neill (November 11, 1931 - January 25, 2022) was an American politician and lawyer. O'Neill was born in Saint Paul, Minnesota. He was in the Minnesota House of Representatives from 1967 to 1970 and in the Minnesota Senate from 1971 to 1976.
